A qualifier value for the specified asynchronous operation(s)._

May be used to determine the target executor to be used when executing this_method, matching the qualifier value (or the bean name) of a specific_{@link java.util.concurrent.Executor Executor} or_{@link org.springframework.core.task.TaskExecutor TaskExecutor}_bean definition._

When specified on a class level {@code @Async} annotation, indicates that the_given executor should be used for all methods within the class. Method level use_of {@link Async#value} always overrides any value set at the class level._@since 3.2
